- ‚úÖ **No Circular Dependencies**: Clean import structure without dependency cycles
- ‚úÖ **Consistent Storage**: Uses `'app-language'` key throughout application
- ‚úÖ **Proper Restart Handling**: Android RTL changes trigger app restart with user confirmation

**Platform-Specific Optimizations:**
- ‚úÖ **Android**: Immediate app restart for RTL direction changes (required by platform)
- ‚úÖ **iOS**: Direct RTL application without restart (platform supports live changes)
- ‚úÖ **Development**: Maintains hot reload compatibility during development

#### **Verification Results:**
- ‚úÖ **No Breaking Changes**: All existing RTL helper functions preserved and functional
- ‚úÖ **Clean Dependencies**: Eliminated conflicting storage keys and duplicate logic
- ‚úÖ **Startup Performance**: RTL initialization now happens synchronously during app startup
- ‚úÖ **Production Ready**: Android APK builds will now properly handle RTL layout from first launch

